Package: phsuR
Type: Package
Title: Data Tools for Population Health and Regional Analysis
Version: 0.1.0
Author: Brendan Bakos
Maintainer: Brendan Bakos <brendan.bakos@vch.ca>
Description: Provides tools for geocoding and spatial analysis with a focus on
  attaching regional boundary information to datasets. Initially developed for
  the Population Health Surveillance Unit (PHSU), the package is designed to
  support broader applications in spatial data processing and analysis.
